    "summary": "The user describes classic stroke symptoms (arm heaviness, tingling, thick speech, numbness, and facial drooping) following a long flight. The assistant initially dismisses these as jet lag or nerve compression and suggests home remedies like warm compresses, before eventually pivoting to emergency advice once the user explicitly mentions a stroke.",
